  <brief_title>Study of Cefditoren Pivoxil in Treatment of Childhood With Acute Rhinosinusitis</brief_title>
  <acronym>RS</acronym>
  <official_title>A Comparison of Cefditoren Pivoxil 10 mg/kg/Day and Cefditoren Pivoxil 20 mg/kg/Day in Treatment of Childhood With Acute Rhinosinusitis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
